{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ef32577bef","title":"军委转发陈毅关于华东军区开展反官僚主义斗争的电报的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"33644269ad","index":0,"year":1953,"month":2,"day":13,"articleId":"ef32577bef"}],"tags":[{"id":"1feb996ca7","name":"陈毅","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bacb455d88","type":"title","text":"军委转发陈毅关于华东军区开展反官僚主义斗争的电报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ef32577bef"},{"id":"c3aa478990","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ef32577bef"},{"id":"24e069d822","type":"appellation","text":"陈毅同志并华东军区党委，并告各大军区、志司和军委各部门：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ef32577bef"},{"id":"59de9fdaad","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）二月十一日陈毅同志给唐亮同志的电报收悉。我们同意这些意见。（二）请各大军区及军委各部门立即注意反官僚主义的问题，其办法就是经常不断地派有威信的负责人员下去检查工作，对严重的官僚主义与违法乱纪的干部展开批判和斗争，最典型者予以惩处。望对此事加以讨论，并作布置。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ef32577bef"},{"id":"8b59267c06","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央军委二月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ef32577bef"}],"page":{"id":"7c2d818c22","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"ef32577bef","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}